), 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{d}{dt}(y^{*}x)=y^{*}\frac{dx}{dt}=y^{*}Ax=(A^{*}y)^{*}x=0,
\]

\end_inset

hence 
\begin_inset Formula $y^{*}x$
\end_inset

